 pieces in mixing bowl and churn <b>1 min\/speed 7<b> while stirring with spatula through hole in mixing bowl lid. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, churn again <b>1 min\/speed 7<b> then transfer to a bowl."},{"content":"Place remaining frozen pieces in mixing bowl then churn <b>1 min\/speed 7<b> while stirring with spatula through hole in mixing bowl lid. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and churn again <b>1 min\/speed 7<b>. Transfer to bowl with ice cream then serve immediately."}],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","13h 15m","8 portions"]}